.TH "get_buffer" 9 "get_buffer" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
get_buffer \- Get the address to store the next image data page.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void *" get_buffer
.BI "(struct memory_bitmap *bm "  ","
.BI "struct chain_allocator *ca "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bm" 12
-- undescribed --
.IP "ca" 12
-- undescribed --
.SH "DESCRIPTION"

Get the address that \fBsnapshot_write_next\fP should return to its caller to
write to.
